    p
      | The customizable prefix mentioned above is the #[code $var-prefix] variable and it's the prefix of all CSS variable names.
      | The variable is located in the #[a(href="https://github.com/angular-package/spectre.css/blob/1.0.x/src/variables/_core.scss" target="_blank") #[code src/variables/_core.scss]] file and its default value is #[code s].
    pre.code(data-lang='SCSS')
      code
        :highlight(lang="scss")
          // src/variables/_core.scss
          // Global CSS variable names prefix.
          $var-prefix: 's' !default;

    p
      | General CSS variable name structure is defined as follows.
    pre.code(data-lang='SCSS')
      code
        :highlight(lang="scss")
          --#{$var-prefix}-#{$name}: #{$value}

